Package: nirs4all
Title: Portable 'nirs4all' Aggregate Binding
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Gregory", "Beurier", email = "gregory.beurier@cirad.fr", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("nirs4all", "contributors", role = c("ctb", "cph")))
Description: Aggregates the 'nirs4all' formats, IO, datasets, methods, 'dag-ml',
    and 'dag-ml-data' language bindings into one portable package surface without
    reimplementing their parsing, numerical, or pipeline logic. The aggregated
    engines remain the source of truth and are delegated to at run time.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://nirs4all.org, https://github.com/GBeurier/nirs4all-lite
BugReports: https://github.com/GBeurier/nirs4all-lite/issues
Depends: R (>= 4.1)
Imports:
    jsonlite,
    yaml
Suggests:
    nirs4allformats,
    nirs4allio,
    nirs4alldatasets,
    n4m,
    dagmldata
Additional_repositories: https://gbeurier.r-universe.dev
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.0
NeedsCompilation: no
